OL,3,CThree escape injury in petrol bomb
OL,4,Cattack on house
OL,6,FPolice have appealed for information
OL,7,Ffollowing reports of a petrol bomb
OL,8,Fattack on a house in Downpatrick.
OL,10,FScorch damage was caused to the front
OL,11,Fof a house in the Pound Lane area
OL,12,Ffollowing in the incident in the early
OL,13,Fhours of Monday.
OL,15,FThree people were inside the property
OL,16,Fat the time but escaped injury.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
