OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782224342
OL,3,CThree escape injury in petrol bomb
OL,4,Cattack on house
OL,6,FA police spokesperson said they
OL,7,Freceived a report at around 12.25am
OL,8,Fthat two men, dressed in dark
OL,9,Fclothing, with hoods up and their
OL,10,Ffaces covered, had thrown a lit item
OL,11,Fat a property in the Pound Lane area
OL,12,Fbefore making off towards John Street.
OL,14,F"Officers attended the scene, along
OL,15,Fwith the Northern Ireland Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service, where the fire had
OL,17,Falready been extinguished by one of
OL,18,Fthe occupants," they said.
