OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782224342
OL,3,CThree escape injury in petrol bomb
OL,4,Cattack on house
OL,6,F"Some damage was caused to the house,
OL,7,Fincluding scorch marks to the front of
OL,8,Fthe property and the front door.
OL,10,F"Three people were in the property at
OL,11,Fthe time. However, no injuries were
OL,12,Freported."
OL,14,FThey added: "Anyone with information,
OL,15,Fincluding CCTV, ring-doorbell or other
OL,16,Ffootage, is asked to contact police on
OL,17,F101, quoting reference number 24 of 22/
OL,18,F06/26."
